:

1. *Napao* je očev automobil, a zatim se uputio na put. (He attacked his father's car, and then set off on a journey.)
2. Prljavi kriminalac *napao* je stariju ženu. (The dirty criminal attacked the elderly woman.)
3. *Napadao* je njene stavove u publici. (He was attacking her views in public.)
4. Svi su bili šokirani kada su čuli da je nepoznati čovek *napao* njenu kuću. (Everyone was shocked when they heard that an unknown man attacked her house.)
5. *Napadnut* je od strane velike gušterice. (He was attacked by a large lizard.)